title: Thao & The Get Down Stay Down (Live on KEXP at Home)
description: Thao & The Get Down Stay Down shares songs performed exclusively for KEXP and joins Morgan live on KEXP on Thursday, July 9, at 3pm PT.

title: Isolated Tracks Episode 1: Cut The Quick by Telekinesis
description: KEXP’s audio producer, Julian Martlew sits down and chats with multi-instrumentalist Michael Lerner, aka Telekinesis. They explore the parts that make up the song "Cut The Quick" from the album "Effluxion".
